---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - The Prompt Shelf" description="About The Prompt Shelf - a curated collection of AI coding rules and prompts.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">About The Prompt Shelf</h1>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-[--color-text-muted] leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        <strong class="text-[--color-text]">The Prompt Shelf</strong> is a curated gallery of AI coding rules and creative prompts.
        We collect, organize, and showcase the best <code class="text-[--color-accent]">CLAUDE.md</code>,
        <code class="text-[--color-accent]">.cursorrules</code>, <code class="text-[--color-accent]">AGENTS.md</code>,
        and image generation prompts from the community.
      </p>

      <p>
        As AI coding tools become essential for developers, having well-crafted rules and prompts makes a huge difference
        in code quality and productivity. But finding good examples is hard - they're scattered across GitHub repos,
        blog posts, and Discord servers.
      </p>

      <p>
        That's why we built The Prompt Shelf: a single, searchable destination where you can discover,
        compare, and copy the perfect AI configuration for your project.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-[--color-text] pt-4">What's included</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
        <li><strong class="text-[--color-text]">CLAUDE.md</strong> - Rules for Claude Code projects</li>
        <li><strong class="text-[--color-text]">.cursorrules</strong> - Configuration for Cursor AI editor</li>
        <li><strong class="text-[--color-text]">AGENTS.md</strong> - Multi-agent orchestration rules</li>
        <li><strong class="text-[--color-text]">Image Prompts</strong> - Midjourney, DALL-E, Stable Diffusion prompts <span class="text-[--color-yellow]">(coming soon)</span></li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-[--color-text] pt-4">Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Built by <a href="https://x.com/yuto_lab_note" target="_blank" class="text-[--color-accent] hover:underline">@yuto_lab_note</a>.
        Suggestions and contributions welcome!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
